Criminal Activity - Theft: Security Supervisor Sean Howell asked for coverage of a female at 8.13.06 as she stated she had forgotten her gift as she left the machine, but when she returned it was gone. A review showed her leaving it beside the machine and a male collecting it and giving it to a female he was with. They wandered the gaming floor and were found in the Guest Smoking area. They were both using Player's cards identifying them as Mike and Kimberly Anstey (PC#635753 and 579376). As they re-entered the gaming floor SS Sean Howell stopped them, taking the gift from the woman. Sean stated they were removed for the evening and they left via Post 2, leaving in a red GMC Sierra truck #HKF 879. Footage was saved to RM2026-54, photos saved to picture storage and IR#2026-282 was created.
